{"tid":1726044,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 一人一個收tvb皮既方法","createTime":"2019-11-16T03:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T09:16:15.000Z","uid":128114,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"79d5c355ffadeac2192f3385e577e674cc915a7b","tid":1726044,"uid":128114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:34:05.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以後都唔入播TVB既食肆</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n罷買廣告雖然有效，但同TVB既新聞報導沒直接既關係，但如果全部黃絲都罷食播TVB既食肆，只要依個風吹到行一行，吹到俾啲酒樓茶記知，為左生意都會肯轉下個個on9新聞台，咁一黎少啲人俾TVB新聞荼毒，二黎啲食客又可以吸收一啲正確啲既資訊。<br />\n最好大家就習慣唔係一開電視就係TVB啦！<br />\n<br />\n無人睇自然無廣告啦！<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"d3517880d8004d0fc7085345ed79684d402c9131","tid":1726044,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:35:07.000Z","msg":"借過位<br />\n11.17〈〈涅槃行動〉〉回血及檢討<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1726003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1726003</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"358d90aadae46c98f6ac5d4538dd5ee915b482fb","tid":1726044,"uid":128114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:39:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5aebaeb37f916dda3b9ad66e54ba092ec2b3a9a8","tid":1726044,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:47:53.000Z","msg":"黎明行動係朝早搞，唔是夜晚搞的。<br />\n［中場檢討］係黎明行動，唔係黃昏行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1725989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1725989</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6b67975f32c4bd7a7ef2fb46dde70bf3abc5ec80","tid":1726044,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b36b8435f782cbd0d16bda7ef0a9219dd04c65","tid":1726044,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcff21c51d8e00ca12fc2a62ab2e518670f40